data.description: Auction Property. PreForeclosure - perfect fix and flip...get your offers in now before it goes to auction.  Atten Investors, This house has some great bones, and a super location, close to the I-4 access.  AC was replaced 5 years ago, roof was approximately 10 years ago.  Some windows were replaced also.  The kitchen is absolutely incredible and is the highlight of this home. it is a HUGE kitchen and huge family room  30 feet by 25 feet with a fireplace. This home features a whole house generator that is hooked to the propane gas tank. Never lose power due to storms. The propane also fuels the stove, oven, and water heater.  With some cosmetics, this home could really be a showplace. It needs complete interior and exterior painting. The seller is motivated.
